## Deployment Commands for VPS

Run these commands on the VPS to deploy the updated website:

```bash
# Step 1: Pull latest changes
cd /var/www/yellowpower-website
git fetch origin
git pull origin main

# Step 2: Navigate to dev directory and rebuild
cd dev
npm install
npm run build

# Step 3: Restart the application
pm2 restart ypi-website

# Step 4: Verify deployment
pm2 status
curl -I http://localhost:3002
```

