## Next Steps After Deployment

### 1. Create Demo Jobs in ERP
Login to ERP at `https://erp.yellowpowerinternational.com`:
- Navigate to: **HR & Personnel â†’ Recruitment â†’ Job Postings**
- Click **"Create Job Posting"**
- Fill in details:
  - Title, Department, Location
  - Job Type (FULL_TIME, PART_TIME, CONTRACT)
  - Description, Requirements, Responsibilities, Qualifications
  - Benefits (optional)
  - Salary Min/Max (optional)
  - **Set Status to "OPEN"** (important!)
- Create 3-5 different job postings

### 2. Test Integration
After creating jobs:
1. Visit `https://yellowpowerinternational.com/careers`
2. Verify jobs appear on the page
3. Click "View All Jobs" - should show all open positions
4. Click on a job - should show details
5. Scroll down and test the application form
6. Submit an application
7. Check ERP â†’ HR & Personnel â†’ Recruitment â†’ Candidates
8. Verify the candidate and application were created

